title: You're Still Going to Get There
itunes:title: You're Still Going to Get There
description:
We all face situations in life that feel like they’re going to derail our purpose. But God wouldn’t have allowed that storm if it was going to keep you from your destiny. Storms may come, but the good news is, God is still in control of the winds.Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love. To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
